No this is not a discussion! I believe this is caused by a bug in:
class org.apache.jasper.compiler.JspUtil {
    public static final String makeJavaIdentifier(String identifier) { }
}

input: bean_message_0
expected: bean_message_0
actual: output: bean_005fmessage_005f0

Our product assume the naming pattern which has been consistent in the previous
revision and was broken by the change.
